title: Kuvings Whole Slow Juicer
description:
For additional information on the featured product please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-2087104/Kuvings+Whole+Slow+Juicer

Delicious, healthful juicing has never been easier. This masticating slow juicer features an extra-wide feed chute that accommodates an entire apple at once, a burly 240-watt motor and an ultra-strong, slow-rotating screw that pulverizes fruits and vegetables for complete juice extraction. 

For more about Sur La Table, visit www.surlatable.com
